==English==

===Adjective===
'''irrecoverable'''

# Not [[recoverable]] or admitting of [[recovery]]; incapable of being recovered: as, an irrecoverable debt.
# That cannot be recovered from or made good; [[irremediable]]; as an irrecoverable disease; irrecoverable danger.

